data: Mr. Brian W. Keller Mr. Brian W. Keller Mr. Brian W. Keller Director of Support Services for the College of Arts and Sciences keller.4@osu.edu 614-292-6801 404 Mendenhall Lab 125 S. Oval Mall Columbus, Ohio 43210 Google Map  I am the Director of Support Services for the College of Arts and Sciences. My staff located in 1199 Physics Research Building are dedicated to supporting the day to day IT needs of the Physics Department. They are also part of the larger team that supports the IT across the college, so we can draw on the collective expertise in the college to address your needs. We support Windows, Mac, and Linux. We also manage the network and support IT for research, administration, and teaching. If you’ve got a problem, question, or comment regarding IT processes, purchasing or support, I would be happy to help.
